鐵站 </span></strong></span><br />\n公投 清洗太子站定旺角站<br />\n太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359a88405c0f7fe499acf909baa6e4c77fec4193","tid":1523361,"uid":176173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2a765ad78fcbc562189b49de4a0b45ed206b3ac","tid":1523361,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"冇人想分化 但佢地今次係抵屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"咁係咪比你屌下手足就可以改變成件事？ 分下輕重啦"},{"pid":"a2b2f1b1e1d995cad381c59cc163433e3e6e9fea","tid":1523361,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:50:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太子831恐襲<br />\n黑警死全家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/125933785285?view=permalink&amp;id=10156177217620286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F125933785285%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D10156177217620286&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=d70a5341\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/125933785285?view=permalink&amp;id=10156177217620286</a><br />\n<br />\n除左黑警同港共政府 記得清算埋黨鐵高層<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523179\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523179</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyzAiYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyzAiYg.png&h=8b18c90d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecc95c08f7e024af84249c8b9f7ee942ec4904c4","tid":1523361,"uid":29820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"咪撚理班傻閪啦 呢家擺明係差佬有問題 仲走去屌班手足 知咩料啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9345bbfd9b2093d7311e2860eef2d27c2e38b7